snippet.title: We Spent 1 YEAR Making a Minecraft RPG Modpack. Here's what we've made.
snippet.description:
I spent one year with 3 developers making the most ambitious Minecraft RPG modpack I've ever made. There are tons of custom bosses, creatures, quests and structures within this adventure modpack called "DawnCraft". It's finally... somewhat finished. Check out the trailer!

Get it here: https://curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/dawn-craft

Get Early Access, Emotes, Cosmetic Armor & Support Pack Development:
https://patreon.com/bstylia14

Join our discord for discussions about DawnCraft: https://discord.com/invite/UjPx5jzd3m

Get a Web-hosted Server for 25% off your first month, and 1-Click Installation of the Serverpack: https://www.bisecthosting.com/bstylia

Big thanks to everyone who made this possible, including Blackcocofish, Nitsu, and all of our patrons.
